I think @AspirinSJL spent some time last week trying to repro this locally unsuccessfully. In any case, it's mac specific (I did try to repro on linux unsuccessfully) and I don't have a mac :(

I can't reproduce either issue locally.

I think we need to try to reproduce it on kokoro mac machine then.
This is currently our top flake. Failure rate is about 19%.

I was able to reproduce locally (it took a while):
`tools/run_tests/run_tests.py -l c++ -c dbg -r 'SingleBalancerTest.SecureNaming[^D]' -n 5000 -j 30`
